3-ne 12:
[center][font_size=26]Shapita 12[/font_size][/center]

[i]Yezu udi ubikila ne upesha bayidi dikumi ne babidi bukôkeshi—Udi uyisha Bena Nefi momumua ne Diyisha dia pa Mukuna—Udi ulaya mabenesha—Malongesha enda adi aya kula ne adi ne mushinga kupita mikenji ya Mose—Udi upesha bantu mukenji bua kuikala bakana bajalama mena bu mudi ya ne Tatuenda bikala bakana bajalama—Fuanyikija ne Matayo 5. Pabuipi ne 34 p.d.K.[/i]

1 Ne biakalua ne pakakula Yezu mêyi â kudi Nefi, ne kudi bavua babikidibua abu, (mpindiewu bungi bua bavua babikidibua, ne bakapeta bukola ne bukôkeshi bua kutambuisha, buvua dikumi ne babidi) ne monayi, wakôlola tshianza tshienda kudi musumba wa bantu, ne wakabila kudibu, wamba: Nudi babeneshibua binuateya ntema ku mêyi a bayidi aba dikumi ne babidi bandi musungula munkatshi muenu bua kunulongesha, ne bua kuikala basadidi benu; ne ndi mubapesha bukola bua ne banutambuisha ne mâyi; ne kunyima kua nuenu batambuishibua ne mâyi, monayi, nenutambuisha ne kapia ne ne Nyuma wa Tshijila; bua nanku nudi babeneshibua binuangitabuija ne kutambuishibua, kunyima kua nuenu bammona ne bamanya ne ndiku.

2 Ne kabidi, nangananga babeneshibua badi aba bitabuija mêyi enu bualu bua nenujadika ne nuamonyi, ne nudi bamanya ne ndi. Eyowa, babeneshibua badi aba bitabuija mêyi enu, ne bâpueka mu ndondu ya didipuekesha ne bâtambuishibua, bualu nebakumbudibua ne kapia ne ne Nyuma wa Tshijila, ne nebapeta dilekedibua dia mibi yabu.

3 Eyowa, babeneshibua badi bapela mu nyuma badi balua kundi, bualu bukalenga bua mu diûlu budi buabu.

4 Ne kabidi, babeneshibua badi bonsu badi badila, bualu nebasambibua.

5 Ne babeneshibua badi batudiji, bualu nebapiana buloba.

6 Ne babeneshibua badi bonsu badi ne nzala ne nyota ya buakana, bualu nebuwula ne Nyuma wa Tshijila.

7 Ne babeneshibua badi bena lusa, bualu nebapeta lusa.

8 Ne babeneshibua badi bonsu badi ne mutshima mukezuka, bualu nebamona Nzambi.

9 Ne babeneshibua badi bonsu benji ba ditalala, bualu nebabikidibua ne bana ba Nzambi.

10 Ne babeneshibua badi bonsu badi bakengeshibua bua bualu bua dîna dianyi, bualu bukalenga bua mu diûlu budi buabu.

11 Ne nudi babeneshibua pânupenda bantu ne pânukengeshabu, ne pânushiminyinabu malu mabi a mushindu onsu, bua bualu buanyi;

12 Bualu nenuikala ne disanka dinena ne nenusangala menamena, bualu difutu dienu mu diûlu nedikala dinena; bualu nanku ki muakakengeshabu bambi bavua kumpala kuenu.

13 Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila ne, ndi nutuma bua nuikala mukela wa buloba; kadi pikala mukela mujimija kutua kuawu, ne batuisha buloba ne tshinyi? Mukela kawakuikala muimpa bua tshintu kabidi to, kadi bua kuipatshibua ne kudiatakajibua mu makasa abu.

14 Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila, ndi nupesha bua kuikala bukenka bua bantu aba. Tshimenga tshiasa pa kakuna katshiena mua kusokokibua to.

15 Monayi, bantu badi batemesha muinda ne ba’uteka muinshi mua tshibondu anyi? To, kadi badi ba’uteka pa mensa a muinda, ne udi ufila bukenka kudi bonsu badi bikala mu nzubu;

16 Bua nanku lekelayi bukenka buenu buengelela bikola kumpala kua bantu aba, bua ne bamona midimu yenu mimpa ne batumbisha Tatuenu udi mu diûlu.

17 Kanuedi meji ne ndi mulua bua kushipa mikenji anyi miaku ya bambi to. Ntshiena mulua bua kushipa to kadi bua kukumbaja;

18 Bualu bulelela ndi nnuambila, katoba anyi kaleta nansha kamua kakena kajimina ku mikenji to, kadi kundi bionsu biakumbajibu.

19 Ne monayi, ndi munupesha mikenji ne mikandu ya Tatuanyi, ne nungitabuija, ne nukudimuna mutshima ku mibi yenu, ne nulua kundi ne mutshima mutshibuluka ne nyuma munyingalala. Monayi, nudi bikala ne mikenji kumpala kuenu, ne mikenji yakumbajibu.

20 Bua nanku luayi kundi ne nupandishibua; bualu bulelela ndi nnuambila ne, pa kumbusha nuenu balama mikenji yanyi, indi munupesha diba edi, kanuakubuela mu bukalenga bua mu diûlu to nansha bishi.

21 Nuvua bumvua ne bantu ba tshikondu tshia kala bakamba, ne bidi bifundibua kabidi kumpala kuenu ne, kushipi muntu to, ne ewu yonsu washipa muntu neikala mu njiwu wa dikosedibua dia tshibawu tshia Nzambi;

22 Kadi ndi nnuambila ne, ewu yonsu udi ufîkila muanabu tshiji neikala mu njiwu wa tshilumbuluilu tshienda. Ne ewu yonsu wambila muanabu ne, Laka, neikala mu njiwu wa kudi tshipangu; ne ewu yonsu wamba ne, Wewa mupota, neikala mu njiwu wa kapia ka mu ngena.

23 Bua nanku, biwalua kundi, anyi ujinga bua kulua kundi, ne uvuluka ne muanenu udi neba tshilumbu—

24 Ndâku kudi muanenu, ne diambedi ulengeja ne muanenu, ne pashisha ulua kundi ne kipatshila kajima ka mutshima, ne nenkuakidila.

25 Umvuangana ne muluishi weba lukasa pawutshidi muikala nenda mu njila, bua kalu kukukuata diba dionsu, ne newedibua mu buloko.

26 Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nkuambila ne, kuakupatukamu to nansha mushindu kayi tô ne pawikala mufuta ne senina wa ndekelu. Ne pawutshidi muikala mu buloko udi mua kufuta nansha senina umua anyi? Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila ne, To.

27 Monayi, bantu ba tshikondu tshia kala bakafunda ne, kuakuenda masandi to;

28 Kadi ndi nnuambila ne, ewu yonsu udi utangila mukaji, bua kumualakana, ukadi mumana kuenda nenda masandi mu mutshima wenda.

29 Monayi, ndi nupesha mukenji ne, kanulekedi bua tshintu nansha tshimua tshia ku bintu ebi tshibuela mu mutshima wenu to;

30 Bualu bidi bitamba buimpa ne nudibengela bintu ebi, bua nanku nenuambula mutshi wenu mutshiamakana, pa mutu pa nuenu kuedibua mu ngena.

31 Bidi bifunda ne, ewu yonsu wipata mukajenda, mulekelayi amupesha mukanda wa dishipa dia dibaka.

32 Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila, ewu yonsu wîpata mukaji wenda, amu bua buendenda, udi umuenzeja kuenda masandi; ne ewu yonsu udi usela mukaji udi mushipa dibaka udi wenda masandi.

33 Ne kabidi bidi bifunda ne, kuditshipi tshianana to, kadi wenzela Mukalenga mitshipu yeba;

34 Kadi bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila ne, kanuditshipi nansha to; nansha kudi diûlu, bualu didi nkuasa wa butumbi wa Nzambi;

35 Anyi kudi buloba, bualu bua budi tshitekelu tshia makasa enda;

36 Kuditshipi nansha ku mutu weba, bualu bua kuena mua kuvuija lusuki lufîka anyi lutoka to;

37 Kadi diakula dieba dikala Eyowa, eyowa; To, to; bualu diakula dionsu didi ditentekeja pa ebi didi difumina ku bualu bubi.

38 Ne monayi, bidi bifunda ne, disu ku disu, ne dinu ku dinu;

39 Kadi ndi nnuambila ne, kanuluanganyi ne bubi to, kadi ewu yonsu wakutûta ku ditama dia tshianza tshia baluma, umuandamuina dikuabu kabidi;

40 Ne biaya neba muntu ku tshilumbuluilu ne kukunyenga tshilamba tshieba, lekela angata ne tshinkutu tshieba kabidi;

41 Ne ewu yonsu wakuendesha kilometre umua, enda nenda kilometre ibidi.

42 Upesha udi ukulomba, ne kupadi udi musua kukusomba tshintu to.

43 Ne monayi bifunda kabidi ne, neunanga mukueba ne ukina muena lukuna neba;

44 Kadi monayi ndi nnuambila, nangayi bena lukuna benu, beneshayi badi banutshipa, enzelayi badi banukina bimpa, ne sambilayi bua badi banumuenena ne badi banukengesha;

45 Bua ne nuikala bana ba Tatuenu udi mu diûlu; bualu udi ubandisha diba dienda bua babi ne bimpa.

46 Bua nanku malu awu avua mikala a mu tshikondu tshia kala, avua muinshi mua mikenji, kundi adi makumbajibua onsu.

47 Malu a kala ajiki, ne malu onsu alu mapia-mapia.

48 Nanku ndi musua ne nuikala bajalama bu mundi mema, anyi bu mudi Tatu wenu udi mu diûlu muikala mujalama.

3-ne 21:
[center][font_size=26]Shapita 21[/font_size][/center]

[i]Isalele neasangishibua palua Mukanda wa Molomo—Bena Bisamba bia Benda nebashikikibua bu mudi bantu badikadila mu Amelika—Nebapandishibua bitabuijabu ne tumikilabu; biobi kabiyi nanku to, nebakoshibua ne nebabutuka—Isalele neibaka Yelushalema Mupia-mupia, ne bisa bijimina nebipingana. Pabuipi ne 34 p.d.K.[/i]

1 Ne bulelela ndi nnuambila ne, ndi nupesha tshimanyinu, bua ne numanya diba dienzeka bintu ebi—dingasangisha mômu bantu banyi, Ô nzubu wa Isalele, ku ditangalaka diabu dia mutantshi mula, ne nenshikika kabidi Siona wanyi munkatshi muabu;

2 Ne monayi, etshi tshidi tshintu tshinganupesha bua tshimanyinu—bualu bulelela ndi nnuambila ne pakumbana bintu ebi bindi nnumanyisha, ne binganumanyisha mema nkayanyi kunyima eku, ne ku bukola bua Nyuma wa Tshijila buanupeshabu kudi Tatu, bimanyibua kudi Bena Bisamba bia Benda bua bamanya bitangila bantu aba badi bikala tshishadi tshia nzubu wa Yakoba, ne bitangila bantu banyi aba bâtangalajibua kudibu;

3 Bulelela, bulelela, ndi nnuambila ne, pâbamanyisha Tatu bintu ebi, ne pâpatukidibua kudi Tatu, biumbukila kudibu ne bilua kunudi;

4 Bualu bidi lungenyi kudi Tatu ne bishikikibua mu bulaba ebu, ne bikala bantu badikadila ku bukola bua Tatu, bua ne bintu ebi bipatukila kudibu bua kulua kudi tshishadi tshia ndelanganyi yenu, bua ne tshipungidi tshia Tatu tshivuaye muenza ne bantu benda tshikumbajibua, Ô nzubu wa Isalele;

5 Nanku, pâpatukila midimu eyi ne midimu yenzeka munkatshi muenu kunyima eku kudi Bena Bisamba bia Benda, iya kudi ndelanganyi yenu yashinguluka mu dipanga dia ditabuija bua bualu bua malu mabi;

6 Bualu nanku bidi bikumbanyina Tatu mbua ne ilopokela kudi Bena Bisamba bia Benda, ne aleja bukola buenda kudi Bena Bisamba bia Benda, bua bualu ebu ne Bena Bisamba bia Benda, bobu kabayi bapapisha mitshima yabu, bua ne bakudimuna mutshima ne balua kundi ne batambuishibua mu dîna dianyi ne bamanya bitupa bilelela bia diyisha dianyi, ne babadibua munkatshi mua bantu banyi, Ô nzubu wa Isalele;

7 Ne pafika bintu ebi, mu mushindu wa ne ndelanganyi yenu neibanga kumanya bintu ebi—netshikala tshimanyinu kudiyi, bua bamanya ne mudimu wa Tatu ukadi mumana kutuadija bua dikumbajibua dia tshipungidi tshivuaye muenza ne bantu badi bikala ba ku nzubu wa Isalele.

8 Ne pâlua dituku adi, nebilua ne bamfumu nebabuikila mikana yabu; bualu bua nebamona tshivuabu kabayi banji kubambila to; ne nebelangana meji pa tshivuabu kabayi banji kumvua to.

9 Bualu mu dituku adi, Tatu neenza mudimu buanyi, wikala mudimu munena ne wa dikema munkatshi muabu; ne nekuikala munkatshi muabu bikala kabayi bawitabuija to, nansha mua bamanyisha muntu.

10 Kadi monayi, moyo wa musadidi wanyi newikala mu tshianza tshianyi; bua nanku kabakumuenzela bibi to, nansha yeya munyanguka bualu buabu. Kadi nemmôndopa, bua mbaleja ne lungenyi luanyi ludi lunena kupita budimu bua diabulu.

11 Nanku nebilua ne ewu yonsu wikala kayi muitabuija mêyi anyi to, mema udi muikala Yezu Kilisto, yenzeja Tatu ne musadidi wanyi atuadila Bena Bisamba bia Benda, ne neamupesha bukola bua ayituadila Bena Bisamba bia Benda, (nebienzeka bu muvua Mose muamba) nebakoshibua ku bantu banyi badi bikala ba mu tshipungidi.

12 Ne bantu banyi badi bikala tshishadi tshia Yakoba nebikala munkatshi mua Bena Bisamba bia Benda, eyowa, munkatshi muabu bu mudi ntambua munkatshi mua nyama ya mu dîtu, bu mudi muana wa ntambua munkatshi mua bisumbu bia mikoku, udi, padiye ubuela mômu udi uyidiata ne uyipandakaja mu bipesa, ne muntu nansha umua kena mua kuyipatuisha to.

13 Tshianza tshiabu netshijudishibua pa mutu pa baluishi babu, ne bena lukuna babu bonsu nebashipibua.

14 Eyowa, diakabi dikala kudi Bena Bisamba bia Benda pa kumbusha bobu bakudimuna mutshima; bualu nebilua mu dituku adi, mudi Tatu wamba, ne nembutula tubalu tuenu munkatshi muenu, ne nennyangakaja matempu enu;

15 Ne nembutula bimenga bia mu bulaba buenu, ne nengûpula miaba yenu mikolesha yonsu;

16 Ne nembutula bu mpaka manga budi mu bulaba buenu, ne kanuakuikala kabidi ne bena lubuku to;

17 Mpingu yenu misonga nembutula kabidi, ne mpingu yenu mimana nempatula munkatshi muenu, ne kanuakutendelela kabidi midimu ya ku bianza bienu to;

18 Ne nenjula bipuka bienu idi munkatshi muenu; nembutula bimenga bienu nanku awu.

19 Ne nebilua ne mafi onsu, ne didinga, ne malakana, ne luntûta lua bungi, ne buakuidi bua mafi, ne masandi, nebijika.

20 Bualu Tatu udi wamba ne, nebilua ne, ne dituku adi bonsu bikala kabayi bakudimuna mutshima ne kuitabuija Muananyi Munanga, bobu nembakosa munkatshi mua bantu banyi, Ô nzubu wa Isalele;

21 Ne nendisombuela ne tshiji tshikola kudibu, kudi bampakanyi, bu mutubu kabayi banji kumvua to.

22 Kadi pikalabu bakudimuna mutshima ne bumvuila mêyi anyi, ne kabayi bapapisha mitshima yabu to, nenshikika ekelezia wanyi munkatshi muabu, ne nebabuela mu tshipungidi ne nebabadibua munkatshi mua tshishadi tshia Yakoba, tshindi mupesha bulaba ebu bua bupianyi buatshi;

23 Ne nebambuluisha bantu banyi, tshishadi tshia Yakoba, ne ba bungi kabidi ba ku nzubu wa Isalele nebalua, bua bibaka tshimenga, tshiabikidibua ne Yelushalema Mupia-mupia.

24 Ne pashisha nebambuluisha bantu banyi, badi bikala bamuangalaka pa mpala onsu wa bulaba, bua ne basangishibua munda mua Yelushalema Mupia-mupia.

25 Ne pashisha bukola bua mu diûlu nebupueka munkatshi muabu; ne nengikala kabidi munkatshi muabu.

26 Ne pashisha mudimu wa Tatu neutuadija dituku adi, mena pâyishibua lumu luimpa elu munkatshi mua tshishadi tshia bantu aba. Bulelela ndi nnuambila ne, dituku adi mudimu wa Tatu neutuadija munkatshi mua bonsu ba ku bantu banyi bavua batangalaka, eyowa, mena bisa bivua bikala bijimina, bivua Tatu mupatula mu Yelushalema.

27 Eyowa, mudimu neutuadija munkatshi mua bantu banyi bonsu bavua batangalaka, ne Tatu nâlongolola njila wa kuluilabu kundi, bua babikila Tatu mu dîna dianyi.

28 Eyowa, ne pashisha mudimu neutuadija, ne Tatu neikala munkatshi mua bisamba bionsu bua dilongolola dia njila wa bantu benda kudisangishabu ku mbelu mu bulaba bua bupianyi buabu.

29 Ne Tatu udi wamba ne, nebapatukila ku bisamba bionsu; ne kabakupatuka mu lubilu to, ne anyi kabakuya ne kunyema to, bualu nenya kumpala kuabu, ne nengikala mulami kunyima kuabu.
